<subSubSection pageId="149" pageNumber="910" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="149.[187,1394,2345,3090]" pageId="149" pageNumber="910">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[190,529,2898,2931]" pageId="149" pageNumber="910">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Widespread but poorly known; records in man-altered habitats suggest a degree of adaptability. Known distribution is somewhat fragmented but would probably be extended by further sampling.
</paragraph>
